 227:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * queue is created, then prvInitialiseMutex() is called to configure the queue
 228:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * as a mutex.
 229:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  */
