 248:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * Macro to mark a queue as locked.  Locking a queue prevents an ISR from
 249:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  * accessing the queue event lists.
 250:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****  */
