2951:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          * It can result in vListInsert() being called on a list that can only
2952:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          * possibly ever have one item in it, so the list will be fast, but even
2953:Middlewares/Third_Party/FreeRTOS/Source/queue.c ****          * so it should be called with the scheduler locked and not from a critical
